00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:56.450
Metastable helium,
pretty much everything

00:20:56.450 --> 00:20:58.690
you can think about
it is forbidden.

00:20:58.690 --> 00:21:03.360
So for a long time,
people believed

00:21:03.360 --> 00:21:04.690
