00:21:41.260 --> 00:21:52.010
But for a long time,
it wasn't even clear

00:21:52.010 --> 00:21:54.110
and the calculations
were not accurate enough

00:21:54.110 --> 00:21:56.740
what was the mechanism by
which the metastable count

00:21:56.740 --> 00:21:58.380
